2. ScriptPubKey (Output Script)
Defined by the receiver
OP_DUP
OP_HASH160
<PublicKeyHash>
OP_EQUALVERIFY
OP_CHECKSIG
ğŸ‘‰ Contains conditions to spend Bitcoin
ğŸ‘‰ Verifies authenticity of the transaction
